          <p class="calc-faq__a">{f.a}</p>
        </details>
      ))}
    </section>

    <section class="cited-sources">
      <p class="t-micro t-micro--saffron">Cited sources</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://pos.toasttab.com/blog/on-the-line/how-to-calculate-food-cost-percentage" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Toast, How to Calculate Food Cost Percentage</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.restaurant365.com/blog/calculate-restaurant-cogs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Restaurant365, Calculating Restaurant COGS</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://restaurant.org/research-and-media/research/economists-notebook/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">National Restaurant Association, Economist's Notebook</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.marginedge.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MarginEdge, Theoretical vs Actual Food Cost</a></li>
